        <chapter>
          <title>Zenefits layoffs</title>
          <paragraph>in May 2015, Zenefits is the fastest growing company in
            Silicon Valley, with 1640 employees. But in November 2015, Buzfeed
            discovers the Macro program allowes not licensed brokers to sell
            insurance. The news is that on February 26th 2016, new CEO David
            Sacks announced 250 layoffs.</paragraph>
